          <h1>VELUX Architects Competition - <br />The Award Winners</h1>

          <div class="md:w-3/4"><p>At the award ceremony on 15th June, in the course of the Daylight Symposium in Basel, Chris Schroeer-Heiermann from Cologne received the first prize for his conversion of a three-party house.</p><h4>Award Documentation 2022</h4>
<a href=https://prospekte.velux.de/prospect/59/velux-architekten-wettbewerb-2022.pdf class="vlx-button secondary" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" onclick="">Download here</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
