                        </div>
                            </a>
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-4">Engelweiss<br /><br /></h3>
                <div class="pb-5 sm:pb-6 text-editor">
                    <p>&bdquo;The bathroom receives warm basic lighting on both sides via the perforated wooden louvre fa&ccedil;ade. This is complemented by the zenith light of the two diagonally offset skylights.&ldquo; </p>
<p>Ansgar Staudt</p>
<p><small>&copy; Mark Niedermann</small></p>
                </div>
