            <a href="#" onclick="">
                        <div class="overflow-hidden aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1">
                            <img src='data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mP8Xw8AAoMBgDTD2qgAAAAASUVORK5CYII=' data-original="//velcdn.azureedge.net/-/media/marketing/de/microsites/aw/velux-aw22-shortlist-dapples-aufstockung-eines-bestandsgebaeudes.jpg?as=true&amp;h=498&amp;w=750&amp;la=en-GB&amp;hash=6D5025343688E5277099B768AD6F8BCF" class="vlx-image lazy" alt="" />
                        </div>
                            </a>
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-4">Dapples, extension of existing buildings</h3>
                <div class="pb-5 sm:pb-6 text-editor">
                    <p>&bdquo;With its gable roof inspired by the mansard roofs of the surrounding houses, the 1960s building continues the legacy of this historic district of Lausanne.&ldquo;</p>
<p>LOCALARCHITECTURE</p>
<p><small>&copy; Michel Bonvin</small></p>
